Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.00,0:02:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(赞斯巴尔之追击！)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.34,0:02:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帝姆舰队在21时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.95,0:02:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在贾布罗准备出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.85,0:02:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以白色基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.75,0:02:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要在出发前二个小时\N先离开这里！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.32,0:02:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要提早二个小时出发？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.19,0:02:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错！呀\N以刚完成的二艘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.76,0:02:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上三艘修理的一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.93,0:02:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们今次让帝姆舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直前去月神二号基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.63,0:02:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但母舰则以反方向\N的轨道前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.73,0:02:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后去攻击目标...\N所罗门基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.44,0:02:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.24,0:02:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色基地将在\N今日19时去太空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.61,0:02:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱少尉，请保重身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.55,0:02:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多谢你，将军\N我会了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.88,0:02:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们放心吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.05,0:02:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当所罗门被攻占后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.45,0:02:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吉翁军便没有军力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.99,0:02:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到时便会向我们\N提出和谈要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.22,0:02:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果这样\N战争便很快结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.26,0:02:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到那时候\N就让我来为你作媒人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.10,0:03:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀...我记得\N你有个未婚夫呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.40,0:03:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.57,0:03:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.81,0:03:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这门亲事是长辈们订的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.78,0:03:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他现在那里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.98,0:03:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了逃避战争\N已去了卫星六号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.58,0:03:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们俩人从未见过面的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.62,0:03:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们回来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色基地准备\N在1小时后出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.26,0:03:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出发前\N大家先作好准备！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.33,0:03:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉！谁是白色基地\N的负责人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.27,0:03:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找他有什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.80,0:03:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我问他在那里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.20,0:03:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布莱特，有人找你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.87,0:03:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是史列加中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.64,0:03:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今后起便调派来母舰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.55,0:03:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱，真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.05,0:03:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？...是真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.28,0:03:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的运气确不错呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.65,0:03:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以和这么美的小姐\N一起工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.56,0:03:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请多多指教，我叫米莱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.42,0:03:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请多多指教！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.70,0:04:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请多多指教！这位小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫雪拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.67,0:04:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看你愁眉不展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.24,0:04:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎为男人的事\N而烦恼呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.91,0:04:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的睡房在那里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.81,0:04:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我们想\N迈向成功的第一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.98,0:04:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关键是各位勇敢的行动上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.45,0:04:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我们地球联邦军\N战胜的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.58,0:04:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到胜利的一刻时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.45,0:04:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位一定会被国民所赞颂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.25,0:04:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为伟大的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在此，我预祝各位\N能够顺利成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.92,0:04:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看他长得那么高大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.49,0:04:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像已死去的\N良哥哥呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过他会一样的仁慈吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.60,0:04:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看他不像是这种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.23,0:04:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们出发了\N快回自己岗位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.10,0:04:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解除所有固定制\N白色基地出发！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.39,0:05:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上空一切正常，打开大门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.23,0:05:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很美呢！         是啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.44,0:05:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在有空闲人的\N可以看看左舷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.87,0:05:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一大群红鹤飞过呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可不可以\N用录影机拍下来？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.24,0:05:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的，我批准吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.65,0:06:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木马号到底去了那里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.45,0:06:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像刚从贾布罗出发了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！我们要快了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.89,0:06:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,30分钟后\N便进入作战距离了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.06,0:06:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劳烦你\N希将军不高兴吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.40,0:06:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.97,0:06:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连我一样也有这种想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.67,0:06:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果这艘赞斯巴尔\N没有新型的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.24,0:06:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毕格罗配备的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.74,0:07:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就别去追木马号了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.21,0:07:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚上校\N那个毕格罗要去看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.88,0:07:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔，带我去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.28,0:07:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要做好准备！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用它来对付普通的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.65,0:07:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论速度和战斗力方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.89,0:07:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是高出好几倍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.32,0:07:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本不是它的对手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.66,0:07:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但只有一个是不够的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.29,0:07:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀！还有两个多姆\N在试验附助器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.73,0:07:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多姆？陆战用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.66,0:07:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！基本上\N加上特别的构造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.67,0:07:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是改良型吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.90,0:07:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事实上\N和以前的相比较好用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.14,0:07:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提高警觉！快作攻击了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.24,0:07:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去集合驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.98,0:07:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道木马号的位置后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.85,0:07:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便开始进攻！         是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.69,0:07:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在后面追来的\N好像是赞斯巴尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果再这样下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.42,0:07:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要20分钟\N便可追上来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.56,0:07:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在应该怎办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.69,0:07:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好极！不用改变航导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.39,0:07:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在E3点开始加速前进\N是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.63,0:08:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照这样看\N母舰便是在航向月球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.97,0:08:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的目的就是这样！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.64,0:08:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚会来的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.40,0:08:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一定会来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.67,0:08:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，你还在吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连检查G战机\N的时间也没有了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.88,0:08:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.11,0:08:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎知道一定是夏亚呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.92,0:08:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...因为母舰\N好像和他有点缘份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.22,0:08:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我...      你怕他吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.42,0:08:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里有人不怕他吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.33,0:08:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,认为如何？米莱？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.80,0:08:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她一定很疲倦了！\N否则不会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.47,0:08:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也相信是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.67,0:08:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木马号突然增加速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.21,0:08:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目标好像是向着月球呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.51,0:08:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月球？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.01,0:08:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想去希莉亚将军\N的古拉拿达？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.91,0:08:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会的\N而且还上当呢！被骗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.52,0:08:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木马是饵，在贾布罗内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.42,0:08:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在一定还有别的舰队\N正在出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.02,0:08:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然这样\N我们回航去攻击他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.29,0:09:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你傻了吗？如果我们回航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木马就会向我们攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.86,0:09:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且只有利用这个机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.93,0:09:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打一场硬仗了！      是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在查知是赞斯巴尔了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.54,0:09:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽可能放大镜头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.97,0:09:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有多久才可攻击？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.34,0:09:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等一会！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2分20秒后\N便有直接攻击过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.65,0:09:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.88,0:09:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,G战机，准备出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.95,0:09:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢坦克，等候命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.32,0:09:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打开各炮门\N打开雷射炮门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.96,0:09:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何官，吩咐\N毕格罗准备出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.20,0:09:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.17,0:09:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有，两个多姆\N亦要出战！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.40,0:09:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何官上尉\N我现在出发了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.98,0:09:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,G翔战机，G战斗机\N准备出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.22,0:10:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绕到母舰后面\N准备迎击敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.89,0:10:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你现在愁眉不展\N似乎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.19,0:10:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你只为何萨比家报复\N才这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我根本就不赞成\N你的做法...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.40,0:10:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,G翔战机出发！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.71,0:10:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,G战机EG型出发！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.88,0:10:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，请你离我远些吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假如在这里遇上攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.62,0:10:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两架也有可能被击中的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.09,0:10:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.83,0:10:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你小心一点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.33,0:10:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假如速度太高\N会被引力吸过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要保持\N适当的速度才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.17,0:10:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你\N我会小心的！来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.54,0:10:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,后面的火箭炮\N快发射掩护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.08,0:10:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.95,0:11:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，看我的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.42,0:11:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很快呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.09,0:11:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们避不过\N毕格罗的高速的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.33,0:11:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威力很强\N但机动力很差呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用雷射炮攻击吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.87,0:11:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道，哥哥在里面吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.88,0:11:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行了，雪拉，快上升！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.92,0:11:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有三台敌方MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.82,0:11:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要钢加农出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.86,0:11:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，叫凯的\N钢加农出动！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.69,0:11:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史列加中尉在那里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.40,0:11:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,噢，有什么事？\N我在控制室下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.67,0:11:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有什么专长？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.50,0:11:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的专长大概是\N战斗机也行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.30,0:11:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然如此\N请你去控制主炮吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.07,0:12:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我有条件的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.91,0:12:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,条件？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.31,0:12:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将白色基地\N开去敌人那边...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.31,0:12:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在驶过去\N应该没问题的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.35,0:12:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这岂不是被敌人追上来？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.52,0:12:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样的话我不做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.89,0:12:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我没自信会打中的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.10,0:12:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听住\N再攻击15秒便停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.44,0:12:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果再攻击的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能连自己人\N也会殃及的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.09,0:12:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真危险...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.89,0:12:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去后面\N用机枪打倒他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.76,0:12:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一于去打，打倒敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.09,0:12:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这艘木马愈来愈成熟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.90,0:13:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是换了舰长吗？不过...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.67,0:13:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该不会是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,普通的市民\N居然演变成军人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.14,0:13:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还可在战舰上作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.71,0:13:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿尔黛西亚...阿尔黛西亚...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.48,0:13:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那时候见到阿尔黛西亚妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.45,0:13:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是穿着军服的\N我不相信...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.92,0:13:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿尔黛西亚最恨就是战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.15,0:13:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她没可能去当军的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.25,0:13:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她根本不会\N在木马上作战的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.66,0:13:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！再过3秒\N就停止用炮攻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.46,0:13:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞄准才发射啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.10,0:13:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起！我不是有意的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.87,0:13:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？布莱特！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.10,0:13:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中尉，恕我不客气说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.61,0:13:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然你年纪比我大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.28,0:13:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但指挥权仍然\N是在我身上的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.74,0:13:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这点我明白的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道就好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.28,0:13:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才要求你\N将母舰回航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.75,0:13:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待我主炮容易发挥作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.65,0:13:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在仍未可以\N再等一会吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.79,0:14:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何不能上升的？\N怎样好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.66,0:14:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火箭炮，发射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.80,0:14:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发射火箭不是这样的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,转过去了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.32,0:14:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看着吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.92,0:14:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也很拚命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.26,0:14:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飞过头很易丢下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.82,0:14:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他居然一点也不怕\N好胆色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.00,0:14:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出现一架好像是机动堡垒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.54,0:14:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢加农准备\N请快出动！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.07,0:14:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凯，你在做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了，刚有问题？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.88,0:14:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在弹射器可以了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.55,0:14:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去帮助掩护雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.98,0:14:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，我现在去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.45,0:15:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将钢坦克固定在出口处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.89,0:15:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要用作炮台的，知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.23,0:15:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，我会告诉准人的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.93,0:15:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色基地\N180度回转！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.24,0:15:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真行，布拉度中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.67,0:15:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的确有头脑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.57,0:15:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你去主炮射击位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.91,0:15:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱小姐\N母舰交给你驾驶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.68,0:15:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.36,0:15:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们在那里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.86,0:15:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不可一直在这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.53,0:15:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真佩服...阿姆罗和雪拉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.88,0:15:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样下去是不行的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我己占了压倒胜优势！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.21,0:16:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收拾你只是时间的问题！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.72,0:16:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉...是凯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.05,0:16:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁有他掩护\N我要变成钢弹作战！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.76,0:16:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何\N先要减低速度...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.23,0:16:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是被击中\N便凶多吉少了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.56,0:16:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过若太慢又危险！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.67,0:16:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！可以进行连接了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.75,0:16:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，你没事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.68,0:16:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，你要快点啊！\N是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，你认为那个驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.22,0:16:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会是什么人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？怎会问起这个的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.53,0:16:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.56,0:16:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，多姆来了！\N小心点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.73,0:16:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！   我没事\N我会想办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.61,0:17:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,G战机已连接妥当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.62,0:17:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士的位置\N已降低了高度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.95,0:17:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以进行攻击了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家注意，准备防御工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.66,0:17:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在没办法\N不用火箭炮自卫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.46,0:17:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家准备攻击\N要一面闪避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.06,0:17:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一面攻击，要瞄准呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.70,0:17:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有30秒进入有效射程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底木马号\N和赞斯巴尔的射程距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.97,0:17:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁会占优势呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.37,0:17:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信只有神才知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.28,0:17:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿尔黛西亚\N你会在木马号内吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.98,0:17:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只得3分钟时间闪避\N知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.99,0:17:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有20秒进入射程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.99,0:17:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有20秒就展开攻击\N唔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.86,0:17:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,15秒...各单位准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.03,0:18:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知这艘母舰\N主炮的威力如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.87,0:18:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们看着吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.20,0:18:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,3，2...1...      好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.77,0:18:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们攻击了！\N还击！   别急！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.41,0:18:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吩咐他们别开炮\N要再近一点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.65,0:18:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火箭炮要连续发射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.89,0:18:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！可以发炮了！发炮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.07,0:18:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们即管看着\N我要打沉你们！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.04,0:18:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！就当我们想冲过去\N冲过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.27,0:18:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.88,0:18:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这比起周围闪避\N更加安全！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.98,0:18:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你即管相信我吧！   是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.41,0:18:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赞斯巴尔完全不闪避\N继续冲过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.35,0:18:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？米莱，快回右驶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.65,0:19:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚，这种打法\N一定是夏亚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.39,0:19:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉说得没错\N一定是夏亚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木马号已经怕了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.37,0:19:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开炮时先要瞄准才好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.44,0:19:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岂有此理！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.22,0:19:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中弹了！      滋味如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.78,0:19:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁叫你们先来攻击母舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.69,0:19:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舰尾火箭炮，快发射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.18,0:19:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还未呢...我不怕的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.75,0:20:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有一台多姆，钢弹呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.76,0:20:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.63,0:20:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果太快，就会失准了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要你知道毕格罗的利害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.11,0:20:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下面好像有物件挂住！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.21,0:20:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道是钢弹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.95,0:20:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...不会的\N凭现时的速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.88,0:20:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他应该已经晕了才对！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.97,0:20:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.68,0:21:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？\N那驾驶员怎会没事的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.72,0:21:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其它的MS和赞斯巴尔呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.53,0:21:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一个多姆已撤退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.86,0:21:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，你没事吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.30,0:21:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何官竟然被他消灭了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.90,0:21:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚上校\N请你准许我出击吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.71,0:21:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别急，他们现在\N已是网中鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.94,0:21:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有很多机会的！   是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.35,0:21:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吩咐他们\N修理被破坏的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.88,0:21:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，为什么\N你会这样说？   咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.92,0:21:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你刚才不是有问我\N驾驶员是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.49,0:21:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看他好像很利害似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.40,0:21:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才这样问而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.16,0:21:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.90,0:21:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在第一阶段总算成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.00,0:21:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错！我们已瞄准\N赞斯巴尔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.17,0:22:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史列加中尉，你真行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.41,0:22:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有你才可击中对方的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.84,0:22:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算得什么呢！\N只是碰幸运气而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.65,0:22:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实你们也很能干呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.71,0:22:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，辛苦大家了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.88,0:22:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次敌人速度\N实在太快了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.19,0:22:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错！\N我当时还真害怕！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.19,0:22:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和赞斯巴尔擦身而过呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.96,0:22:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一定是夏亚\N的作战方法！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.26,0:22:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚？         唔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.19,0:22:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种战法其它人\N一定不够胆用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.26,0:22:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真佩服你呢\N雪拉小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.07,0:22:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你击落了一架MS\N真能干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.00,0:22:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别这么说...\N我也是好运而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.01,0:22:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太谦虚了\N我一看就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.54,0:22:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的技术是一流的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.04,0:22:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是了，我现在想先洗个澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.65,0:22:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只余5分钟时间啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.32,0:22:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人很快会回头的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.88,0:22:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了\N米莱小姐你去不去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.95,0:22:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你自己去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.55,0:22:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！是！我们去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.62,0:22:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我们去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.89,0:22:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又去！

